# Heritage Category Card
# -----------------------------------------
<HeritageCategoryCard@MDCard>:
    size_hint: None, None
    size: dp(110), dp(36)
    md_bg_color: 0.15, 0.15, 0.15, 1
    radius: [15, 15, 15, 15]
    elevation: 3
    orientation: "horizontal"
